        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'The Outlook inbox has a 47-message thread from the Audit Committee Chair regarding the 12 governance findings. Using Copilot, summarise the thread in 6 bullets covering: which findings the Audit Committee considers most material, which findings the Audit Committee considers already remediated, the 3 outstanding requests, the proposed remediation timeline, and the next reporting cycle. Then draft a single reply that responds to all 3 outstanding requests, confirms the remediation timeline, and proposes a 30-minute follow-up call. Apply Audit Committee formal style.'}
